title: Venus Williams rallies to advance to 2nd round in Hong Kong
text:
> Top News Venus Williams rallies to advance to 2nd round in Hong Kong Venus Williams of the United States hits a return shot against Yuliya Beygelzimer of Ukraine at the WTA Hong Kong Open Tennis tournament in Hong Kong, Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015. (AP Photo/Kin Cheung)
